claim: R. Kelly is known for hit album "Bump N' Grind."
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is known for a collection of major hit singles including `` Bump N ' Grind '' , `` Your Body 's Callin ' '' , `` I Believe I Can Fly '' , `` Gotham City '' , `` Ignition  (  Remix  )  '' , `` If I Could Turn Back the Hands of Time '' , `` The World 's Greatest '' , `` I 'm a Flirt  (  Remix  )  '' , and the hip-hopera `` Trapped in the Closet '' .
